cs.HC, cs.IR, cs.MM, cs.CV, cs.SD

The paper focuses on designing a web browser that optimizes power consumption for OLED displays on mobile devices. This involves adapting the color schemes of web pages to reduce power consumption. Therefore, the most likely category is Human-Computer Interaction (cs.HC) as the paper deals with user interaction with a web browser. Information Retrieval (cs.IR) is also likely as the paper discusses optimizing web content for OLED displays. Multimedia (cs.MM) and Computer Vision (cs.CV) are possible categories as the paper deals with color optimization for displays. Finally, System and Control (cs.SD) is a possible category as the paper discusses reducing system power consumption.
